OL,4,G0205FOffended By Irvine Welsh
OL,5,     GThe novelist explores the topic
OL,6,     Gof offense as he discusses the
OL,7,     Grisk of upsetting people in the
OL,8,     Gcurrent climate. Strong language
OL,9,     Gfrom the start and scenes which
OL,10,     Gsome may find offensive.
OL,11,G0300FUnmuted
OL,12,     GNatalie Gayle explores the first-
OL,13,     Gever London Mural Festival. Sam
OL,14,     Gmeets BAFTA award-winning artist
OL,15,     GGraham Fink. Also, a look at the
OL,16,     Glegacy of the late MF DOOM.
